STEP 1: SOFTEN GREEN CANDY MELTS AND SPOON MELTED MIXTURE AROUND TOP RIM OF 4-6 GLASSES. ALLOW CANDY MELT TO DRIP DOWN THE SIDE OF THE GLASSES.

INTO EYE CUP & TOP WITH ORANGE CREAM AND SPRINKLES.
